conda activate orb-trading

python main.py --mode train --api-key 31ToiHyQcmF3tx0u9alvjiF5IjTrqSSR --symbol QQQ --start-date 2023-02-01 --end-date 2024-02-29


How to Use the System

Training Phase:

python main.py --mode train --api-key 31ToiHyQcmF3tx0u9alvjiF5IjTrqSSR --symbol QQQ --start-date 2023-03-23 --end-date 2025-03-24
This will create a pattern recognition model based on historical data.
Backtesting:

python main.py --mode backtest --api-key YOUR_POLYGON_API_KEY --symbol QQQ --use-ai
This will test the strategy on historical data to evaluate performance.
Optimization:
python main.py --mode optimize --api-key YOUR_POLYGON_API_KEY --symbol QQQ --use-ai
This will find the best strategy parameters.
Live Trading:
python main.py --mode live --api-key YOUR_POLYGON_API_KEY --symbol QQQ --use-ai
This will monitor the market in real-time for ORB setups.